Chartio self-service business intelligence cloud software

Chartio is a cloud-based business analytics solution on a mission to enable both data analysts and business users (in marketing, sales, operations, finance) within an organization to access, explore, transform and visualize their data. Chartio is a great fit for companies in software, e-commerce, transportation, logistics, distribution, media & entertainment sectors that have to rely on data to succeed in their business. Chartio works with any SQL database or data warehouse in the cloud including Microsoft SQL Server and Azure.

Chartio's benefits for data teams include:
- Build complex SQL queries quickly and efficiently via a visual interface
- Get to see and review the generated SQL code
- Show the love from your organization by empowering every team to analyze their data on their own
- Get back time to focus on more complex analyses and models

Chartio's benefits for business teams include:
- Get to insights in minutes, not weeks
- Access and explore all your data without having to wait on your data team
- Create powerful charts, reports and dashboards for everyone in your team
- No need to learn SQL or any other proprietary language to explore your data
